Essential Systems and Services
Automation
Automation or automatic control, is the use of various control systems for operating equipment such as machinery, processes in factories, boilers and heat treating ovens, switching on telephone networks, steering and stabilization of ships, aircraft and other applications with minimal or reduced human intervention. Some processes have been completely automated.

 

The biggest benefit of automation is that it saves labor; however, it is also used to save energy and materials and to improve quality, accuracy and precision.The term automation, inspired by the earlier word automatic (coming from automaton), was not widely used before 1947, when General Motors established an automation department. It was during this time that industry was rapidly adopting feedback controllers, which were introduced in the 1930s.

Automation has been achieved by various means including mechanical, hydraulic, pneumatic, electrical, electronic devices and computers, usually in combination. Complicated systems, such as modern factories, airplanes and ships typically use all these combined techniques.

Instrumentation

ESS-Middle east embrace a total systems approach to meet the growing operational & environmental monitoring demands of the Oil & Gas, Petrochemical & Power sector industries. 

We offer products & services which are technically proven in the field,  well supported by qualified service personnel & most economical with excellent return of investment.  

Services

ESS-Middle east employs highly qualified and experienced engineers who are available locally in Qatar to provide Design Assistance, Installation Supervision, Commissioning and Testing at site if required by the customer.  Training, Technical support & Emergency services are available throughout the year. We supply spare parts and the appropriate support services for Company supplied products and systems.

 

We offer following services:

 

  • System Integraion (Analyzers & Automation systems)

 

  • Calibration & Testing 

 

  • Monitoring services (Emissions, Air Quality & Water Quality)

 

  • Temperature Mapping (Thermal Imaging & Temperature Dataloggers)

 

  • Installation & Commissioning 

 

  • Instrument Rentals (Portable Flue Gas analyzers & Air Quality instruments)

 

Send your queries to service@essme.com
